Summary: GameBox is a beginner-friendly Python package built on top of pygame, designed to make 2D game development faster and easier. It provides ready-to-use modules, utilities, and abstractions that let new developers create polished games without needing advanced coding knowledgeâ€”while still offering the flexibility for experienced coders to customize and extend.
